NB. rws
NB. Rows weighted sum
NB.
NB. Syntax:
NB.   sum=. weight rows rws array
NB.
NB. Application:
NB. - to subtract from row 3 twiced row 4:
NB.   ((1 _2) 3 4 rws (i. 5 5)

