NB. 0 0 10 11                      0 0 10 11
NB.    1 tru i. 3 4                   _1 tru i. 3 4
NB. 1 2  3                         0 1  2  3
NB. 0 6  7                         4 5  6  7
NB. 0 0 11                         0 9 10 11
NB.    1 tru i. 4 3                   _1 tru i. 4 3
NB. 1 2                            0 1  2
NB. 0 5                            3 4  5
NB.                                0 7  8
NB.                                0 0 11

tru=: (<:~ 0&<.) tr trucut

